{
  "stem": "20686.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 17 SECONDS] Now, I go here to after-- this is the liquidation of the ghetto. 'Two more long years went by.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Years of threat and pain, from hunger blossomed death like grass after rain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And yet, [? we ?] [? live ?] [? with ?] hope, nourished by a delirious dream of a heroic messiah who speeds from the east to redeem, and the ghetto buzzed with rumors spread by starving Jews, figments of imagination.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Dazzling felicitous news, news of gigantic battles, deliverer is coming, is here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, how sweet the smell of this lie, how bitter the truth to fear.' That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I began-- I actually wrote some poetry in camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And funny enough, there was no paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got hold of a little bit of a-- a pencil.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to write on my hand, and read it to myself, I tried to memorize it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I did some of it, I did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I-- I wrote it after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was so-- it was not-- it was not-- it was not the thing I wanted to-- what I wanted-- It was the thing I wanted to say.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the form was not-- was only sort of limping behind the idea.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was born in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was born in 1940-- 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now here I'm-- I'm telling you. 'Then came summer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A dark date to remember, the year 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's the 5th of September.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That morning we were greeted by white placards with black news.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mothers, Germany demands your children, all sick and elderly Jews, they are to be resettled in another place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans has sworn to it by their holy grace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do not obstruct this, mothers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bring your children freely.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
